headline.main: 30 WRECKS BLOCK HARBOR AT NARVIK; Fleeing British Captains of Merchant Ships Say Nazis Will Bomb Railway

lead_paragraph: STOCKHOLM, Sweden, May 2-- --Wrecks of approximately thirty naval and merchant ships in the only part of Narvik Harbor shallow enough for anchorage have ruined it as a port, four captains of British merchant ships agreed today.
